Katie Amess https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katie_Amess 0 Katie Amess (born 19 July 1985 in Basildon, Essex, England) is an English actress and model. She is the eldest daughter of Conservative MP Sir David Amess. She is known as the host of British TV commercials and from several film and TV roles.
